id":"59efb974dacd077d06b45c9bc45cbf154b8ecf0c","tid":1929004,"uid":201319,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8e9e3606f2e2ad298ec876ebde7760f0afdc13a0","tid":1929004,"uid":125429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5592128c32333dbd911a2e9e20168878a7848737","tid":1929004,"uid":201319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T22:30:43.000Z","msg":"聽朋友講而家NLP基本上係都做deep learning<br />\n而且有好多問題都considered &quot;solved&quot;<br />\n例如你有billions既label data, train一個夠大夠多layer既neural network<br />\n已經係state-of-the-art既model<br />\n如果係真既話真係有可能唔洗點識寫code<br />\n因為而家google就係想整到deep learning任何人都寫到<br />\n佢地係度推自己個TensorFlow, define個model一至幾行code, training一行code, testing一行code<br />\n<br />\n舊d比較base on stat idea既approach唔知仲有冇人用<br />\n因為講到而家deep learning幾咁屈機恐怕好難講<br />\n同聽過做NLP research d人都可能要轉行做其他野<br />\n<br />\n呢類course外國應該有U會放上網public俾人睇<br />\n我google左下搵到有呢個<br />\n<a href=\"http://web.stanford.edu/class/cs224n/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.stanford.edu%2Fclass%2Fcs224n%2F&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8HWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=d00292de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://web.stanford.edu/class/cs224n/</a><br />\n佢地好似有upload埋上YouTube<br />\n可以俾你fd睇一睇覺得點先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T00:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:56:32.000Z","msg":"如果我fd講既係真既話, 咁我覺得翻譯真係有機會會被machine取代<br />\n而家deep neural network已經可以generate好高quality既speech signal, 連tone/emotion都可以gen到好natural<br />\n我會expect如果關aesthetic事既話(例如書, d句子譯得靚唔靚), 可能deep learning暫時未做到<br />\n但係純意譯既話可能淨係要個人黎double check一下就OK<br />\n<br />\nbtw個人對master program有d偏見<br />\n覺得除非係出名既U/program, 或者真係有人confirm有公司care<br />\n唔係既話都唔好讀, 有錢另計<br />\n因為master program主要就係開黎賺錢, 好多時教既野根本就係undergrad level<br />\n<br />\n就咁睇個program d course, 我自己唔係好識NLP, 所以純粹感想黎<br />\n會有bias, 唔好take it too serious<br />\n1. Computer programming in Python<br />\n呢科應該OK, 而家Python dominate咁制, 例如上面講deep learning, TensorFlow, 係Python度train network已經好簡單<br />\nPython本身好處係易寫易睇, 唔好處係同其他language例如C++比可能會慢d, depends on application<br />\n<br />\n2. Corpus Linguistics in R<br />\n以我所知R主要stat既人用, 我其實唔識, 但係我會覺得R做到既野Python都做到<br />\n所以最好問下d兩樣都熟既人問下意見<br />\n同埋唔知industry d人係咪care你要識R, 定Python已經好夠<br />\n<br />\n3. Machine translation and other natural language processing applications<br />\n佢話using statistics, 有可能係Hidden Markov Model個d<br />\nR入面有build-in tools做parameter estimation<br />\n(但我相信Python都有人整左library, 因為佢既popularity)<br />\n另一個問題係, machine translation同其他application會唔會已經outperformed by deep learning<br />\n係既話識呢d old technique未必有用<br />\n不過外面老一輩既可能淨係識同用緊呢d, 佢地可能會care<br />\n<br />\n4. Computational Linguistics<br />\n呢個可能係講下language有咩property, grammar點拆之類<br />\n其中一個我聽人講過既係d vocabulary有linear structure, 例如你可以represent d vocabulary做high dimensional vector (或者係a point in a high dimensional space)<br />\n例如{man}, {female}, {king}, {queen}各自對應high dimensional space既points, {king}+({female}-{man})對應個點係好接近{queen}個點<br />\n<br />\n5. Translation tools for professional translators<br />\n&quot;Using computer tools&quot;呢句令我覺得係學用現成software<br />\n<br />\n6. Machine learning for language processing<br />\n呢個聽落似係用會deep learning, classification, gen summary呢有用開deep learning<br />\n我相信state-of-the-art都係用deep NN<br />\n所以呢科我覺得有用<br />\n<br />\n7. Research methods and professional skills<br />\n似吹水"},{"pid":"828a9a2c77010dda5a0d2f44f775448ad5d49502","tid":1929004,"uid":125429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59efb974dacd077d06b45c9bc45cbf154b8ecf0c","tid":1929004,"uid":201319,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8e9e3606f2e2ad298ec876ebde7760f0afdc13a0","tid":1929004,"uid":125429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5592128c32333dbd911a2e9e20168878a7848737","tid":1929004,"uid":201319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T22:30:43.000Z","msg":"聽朋友講而家NLP基本上係都做deep learning<br />\n而且有好多問題都considered &quot;s